UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2304
1 AN ACT relating to criminal justice.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 610.130 is amended to read as follows:
4 (1) Unless otherwise exempted, an appeal to the Circuit Court may be taken as a matter
5 of right from the juvenile session of the District Court from dispositional orders
6 under KRS 610.110.
7 (2) The appeal authorized by this section shall be taken as[in the manner] provided in
8 the Rules of Criminal Procedure, and the Circuit Court shall, in the best
9 interests[interest] of the child, hear the appeal[such cases] expeditiously.
